# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Project-Specific Notes
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The following directories are preserved with .gitkeep files:
# - data/saves/     (for game save files)
# - data/logs/      (for application logs)
# - data/config/    (for configuration files)
# - third_party/    (for external dependencies via git submodules)

# To preserve an empty directory, create a .gitkeep file:
# touch data/saves/.gitkeep
# git add data/saves/.gitkeep

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# End of .gitignore
